Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部隊強行突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:02.58,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1\blur3}翻譯 洛艾妖 十八 斑馬線 校譯 洛艾妖 時間 倉鼠  後期 風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點離開那裡 小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人攻過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉決裂了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙… 居然連這個都有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官應該馬上就會到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官來了的話我會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人質在413室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法把人給救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是認真的嗎 沒得到上級的許可就強行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回警署去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課…課長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃掉的話會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻！ 休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝將成為我的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人質了 雪輝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢動我就殺了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢動我就引爆它！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就炸飛一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分後引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這多少能起點障眼法的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不認為這樣就能迴避得了DEAD END
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能逃一步算一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 交易是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻 我會放了雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但與此相對的 你也要扔掉那個危險物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小雪給了我這個本來就已經死掉的人未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當你未來的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們長大了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還不快點長大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成大人的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點變成大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪是我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果連這個也無法實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我為了小雪而死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死了 我也會繼續追著小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙就在這裡和我一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和由乃一起去看星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美彌音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於抓到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝那傢伙用了那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\3c&HA74856&}命運的枷鎖又將兩個人聯繫到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛有光…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是閃光彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有些晃眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實彈給他的話有點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這還是晃眼而已麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 剛剛爆炸的是在四樓 是我安裝的炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙沒死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧遇到你 我想到了避開這個DEAD END的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真是走狗屎運啊 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得在其他警察趕來之前 把你們殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話一切問題就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 雪輝 你是不會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想再開一次槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可是對著我妻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍扔了 不然我就切掉我妻的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點 如果你自己掛了可就什麼都撈不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4th
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備怎麼做 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍的話 萬一失手由乃就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說都會有命中由乃的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看未來日記…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}子彈射中由乃 由乃中彈身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話不就不能開槍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\frz46.408\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\move(430,347,430,74)\shad0}小雪開槍了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\frz45.055\move(552,397,552,125)}小雪開槍把我打死了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\frz45.428\move(670,404,664,142)}天野雪輝將2ND射殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍的話會擊中由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記上寫著不好的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色鐵青呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是扔下槍的話 我們也會被殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被小雪射死也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能為小雪而死的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是說謊 小雪也曾說過我們是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是假裝也陪我參加了結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼鬼幸福 我才沒閒工夫陪你們玩戀愛遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要隨身帶著這樣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃不想要變得更加幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是個超級跟蹤狂 追著我有一年了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想成為新娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒辦法實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有小雪一個人也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！別說什麼沒辦法實現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會給由乃幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算由乃放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會放棄的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逞強了 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻會變成怎樣都無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…喜歡由乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能死！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警察 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為神的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為神的話… 我就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 課長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島狩人事件還有栽贓雪輝一行人的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美彌音已經全部都交代了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算相信恐怖分子嗎 西島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你做個交易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從一開始就沒有攻擊你的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察的情報我也會繼續洩露給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放下武器吧 課長 我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不是警察了 只是個犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有調查權限的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法預知搜查日記了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未來日記被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(434,164)\frz5.667\shad0\c&H92A342&\3c&HFFFFFF&}無警察情報。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\frz5.667\shad0\c&H92A342&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(412,270)}被雨流美彌音的槍所射殺。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老婆和孩子怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸前勉強救出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這是我任性的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你能再次與我結盟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子就拜託你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啊 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不覺得這是道歉就能解決的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}6/13 20:10 子彈射中由乃 由乃中彈身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}6/13 20:11 4th射中我 我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}6/13 20:11 避免DEAD END
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 整件事情的處理就拜託給了西島警官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我和由乃也被嚴厲地追究了責任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據來須先生所留下的「真相」資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的誤解被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他是否已經預知到了這個結局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}櫻見事件！ 在職警官所引發的不詳時間！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官的事件在世間引起了轟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有報道我們的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 9th好像也逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 都這個時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可喜可賀的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我打中的警察保住了性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後要怎麼辦呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我想先到爸爸那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借望遠鏡用用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後登上高地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人生有最完美的happy end的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計就是像今天這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你也太誇張了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 我真想讓這個瞬間變成永遠 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻也稍稍熟練些了嘛 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別取笑我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您撥打的電話暫時無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫不上爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車來了哦 我們跑過去吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有點時間 我去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便買點飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\shad0\frz4.293\move(781,256,777,30)}最好遠離我妻。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\shad0\frz2.661\move(349,335,346,111)}為了調查案情，警察正在搜尋她，但是她現下落不明。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋瀨…或
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\shad0\frz3.203\move(672,427,672,310)}一定要多加小心。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 還你手機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好像有短信來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是條垃圾短信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行李不能少帶點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 裡面有重要的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多必要的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內衣啊 毛巾啊 藥啊 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}ココロが死ぬよ　自分のためないが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}心已不隨己地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}引き金になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}做拋磚引玉之用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:48.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}助かる君えと　信じて君からもれだ声に呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:48.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}被我所信任的 拯救我的你之聲所呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:54.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}奇跡を　いもの追っか駆ける悲劇は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:54.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}那奇跡 那追逐虛像而去的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}終わらないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}永無終止之日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:05.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}闇の奥で繰り返す叫び いとに痛み悪意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:05.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}在黑暗泥沼中不斷的吶喊 及那深沉的惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:09.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}選ばれしだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:09.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}這就是被選中的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}泣きたくない　これ以上愛たくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}不願再哭泣 再不願去愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:17.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}燃える　愛しいさが通差した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:17.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}燃燒的愛意卻穿體而過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:21.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}愛きて　泣きたく追い駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:21.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}抹掉淚水 去追逐那愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}誰にも　止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}誰都無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}これは未来　それとも夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.25,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}此乃未來 抑或是夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}答えは何処だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}答案不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:38.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}これが今を　試す扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:38.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}若此為如今的試煉之門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}壊すは開けれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}毀滅也無法將其開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}どしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}該如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.68,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEC00C1&\move(665,31,545,31)}姆魯姆魯{\c&H5B6F5D&}老師的{\c&HFBF9F9&}秘密未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.68,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz359.479\fs32\c&HE85239&\move(554,320,523,320)}4th{\c&HFCFCFC&}的{\c&H240BB9&}由來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.68,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H073027&\fs35\c&HFDFAFC&\pos(616,479)}來須圭悟篇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}4/21 10:23 咖啡屋「隱居」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:22:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 你也被選為12位日記所有人之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的維也納咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣 請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要手辦模型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈模型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的傢伙都說扎古比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是比較喜歡鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比起鋼彈更…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這就是我成為警察的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我後來把它偷到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之的意思是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來被老爸發現狠K了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就成了警察
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過當時老爸也幹起了小偷的勾當
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事看來會很長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到工作的老爸人間蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後搞垮身體死在了路邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒人去揍老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了揍人才成為警察的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查日記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就心懷感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我自己一人也能揍得了人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香腸還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}於是姆魯姆魯把維也納咖啡（Wiener Kaffee）想成香腸和咖啡兩樣了。日語中香腸也就是Wiener。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名設定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}匿名設定就是設置不讓對方知道自己的電話號碼。
